      "name": "case-44",
      "src": "# scribe.word — drafts the Word from your intent, grounded in what's there; never presses (see-only,\n# the express is yours to sign). Descends from able.word.\n\nA scribe is an able.\nA scribe can see ables.\nA scribe can see operations.\nA scribe can see tools.\nA scribe needs llm cognition.\n",
