        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "case-45",
      "src": "# cherub.word — the gate, right below I. Processes the three BE ops (birth/connect/release) and summon:mate — a connected name births its first top-level being through cherub, owned by the name. Descends from able.word.\n\nA cherub is an able.\nA cherub can do grant-able:human.\nA cherub can do grant-able:global.\nA cherub can call mate as receiver.\nA cherub can be birth.\nA cherub can be connect.\nA cherub can be release.\nA cherub needs scripted cognition.\nA cherub never wakes.\n",
      "ir": [
        {
          "kind": "is",
